title: Dracula 4 v1.0.0 Android
description:
The Museum sends the art restorer Ellen Cruz to authenticate the painting. She never would have imagined that such a mission would take her across Europe in the wake of the portrait of the famous Prince of Wallachia, Vlad Tepes. 
's Young suffers from a serious illness. Budapest to Istanbul, she follows the trail of paint and plunges into a conflict between the first vampire and "Shadow of the Dragon", a secret order who dreams of producing a new breed of creatures, free from the clutches of Dracula.
